title: NCUA, Credit Unions in Texas, Oklahoma and Lower Mississippi states, USA, 2008
name: NCUA, Credit Unions in Texas, Oklahoma and Lower Mississippi states, USA, 2008
description:
The point shapefile shows locations of credit unions across Texas, Oklahoma and States in the Lower-Mississippi Delta area. 
According to National Credit Union Administation (NCUA), nearly all Credit unions are relatively safe compared to major banks. 
Therefore on 25th Nov 2008, Treasury said that  credit unions will not be part of TARP. Instead Treasury has decided to offer nearly $2.5 bill in low interest
loans to credit unions through NCUA.
